331
00:30:45,246 --> 00:30:46,666
What am I waiting for?

332
00:30:56,010 --> 00:30:59,402
Mr. Shi, how afraid are you that others will find your WeChat account?

333
00:31:05,711 --> 00:31:07,012
(I'm home.)

334
00:31:08,215 --> 00:31:10,522
