446
00:39:24,480 --> 00:39:26,402
(Okay, thank you very much.)

447
00:39:26,483 --> 00:39:27,503
Okay.

448
00:39:34,806 --> 00:39:36,436
Can I pursue you?

449
00:39:45,278 --> 00:39:46,909
