469
00:40:45,810 --> 00:40:47,242
I'm fine with that.

470
00:40:47,643 --> 00:40:48,743
What about you?

471
00:40:49,166 --> 00:40:50,507
That's fine with me.

472
00:41:11,486 --> 00:41:12,926
You seemed out of sorts just now.

473
00:41:13,031 --> 00:41:14,446
