474
00:41:20,926 --> 00:41:22,765
(Mr. Shi, it's urgent.)

475
00:41:22,886 --> 00:41:24,802
(You confirmed my draft yesterday.)

476
00:41:24,883 --> 00:41:26,914
(Please send me a confirmation as soon as possible.)

477
00:41:31,449 --> 00:41:33,999
